Blow me down!

57
00:03:09,430 --> 00:03:12,570
Now who coulda' known
that football is my game?

58
00:03:12,570 --> 00:03:16,350
Aye, and there's the
fine ship I've always wanted.

59
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,610
Wait a minute, guys.

60
00:03:17,610 --> 00:03:18,830
This isn't right.

61
00:03:18,830 --> 00:03:20,700
It's too perfect.

62
00:03:20,690 --> 00:03:23,330
Yeah, ain't it just?

63
