76
00:04:05,990 --> 00:04:08,400
♪ No, no, don't go astray ♪

77
00:04:08,410 --> 00:04:11,550
♪ No, no, we mustn't stay ♪

78
00:04:11,540 --> 00:04:16,750
♪ If we do we'll rue the day ♪

