86
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:33,740
No!

87
00:04:33,730 --> 00:04:36,100
No, don't make me do it
Somnambula.

88
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:37,980
What you're doing is evil.

89
00:04:37,990 --> 00:04:41,030
I have my youth back
I have my new powers.

90
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:44,660
